{"tid":535232,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好享受一直暗戀人","createTime":"2018-01-20T15:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T09:26:50.000Z","uid":167824,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"718eb9e18798a8cea4a43597e9395df68971859f","tid":535232,"uid":167824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:34:49.000Z","msg":"D人話暗戀男神/女神好痛苦<br />\n但我自己就好享受暗戀人嘅過程<br />\n或者可能係自己有d苦中作樂<br />\n但每次見到暗戀嘅人就好開心<br />\n個人就好有動力<br />\n好似人生有左色彩，有左意義<br />\n可能你會問點解我唔行前一步<br />\n但有時候我暗戀到分唔清我鐘意真實既佢<br />\n定係我想像中既佢<br />\n再加上自己冇咩優點<br />\n無謂害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n在此<br />\n多謝男神A你的出現<br />\n令到我呢半年過得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (雖然都係我自己ff)"},{"pid":"7966419d8bd63581d4d03a26b8112dd2597ed4cc","tid":535232,"uid":19867,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:36:57.000Z","msg":"試都唔試下 咁好咩"},{"pid":"8b14396359df3ede1a5f2ca7f1089b538a3928e9","tid":535232,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:36:59.000Z","msg":"從來暗戀只有自己知 享受最曖昧時"},{"pid":"1ca410300ec409f6fa76f5774dee1e943e8f246c","tid":535232,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:38:41.000Z","msg":"冇人俾我暗戀"},{"pid":"a15d0f7725029c3c062110d3d6d63b4e9fa91538","tid":535232,"uid":105715,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:39:59.000Z","msg":"我仲發覺到，火雞既味道，未食同食第一啖之間，已經係最高峰既味道。之後，不過就係食開就食埋落去咁解﻿。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DlmBMIOxvsI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDlmBMIOxvsI&d=VTVUaDvxTuXSvhzJp1u6BzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f6df7ecb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DlmBMIOxvsI</a>"},{"pid":"8194075c237d35458e9536a36abe89f718a4a0c6","tid":535232,"uid":143307,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T15:40:47.000Z","msg":"曖昧最好 暗戀食屎<br />\n<br />\n曖昧<br /